{"tid":1199734,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"打唔贏 不如智取","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T14:40:24.000Z","uid":225481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4cab139140c252d3a2fc7304e12e682ecb95423","tid":1199734,"uid":225481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打提過警員編號查詢系統（<a href=\"http://police-github.github.io/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpolice-github.github.io%2F%EF%BC%89&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=5cba59cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://police-github.github.io/）</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人一齊諗下點運用係11/12號？ 打就一定打唔贏佢地架啦， 我地諗下點智取仲好啦。<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為如果當場叫到佢地個名，幫佢拉離警察個角色，點都有d幫助嘅。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係撞上黑警，都容易起返佢底，搵返佢出黎屌。<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有無咩好運用方法或者智取嘅方法對付警察？"},{"pid":"65f078e0724ae13499b938387027212fb9f531ef","tid":1199734,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}